channel.description:

Ok I found this piece of gold. I love rs fan movies (Like world 901) and this didn't disappoint me either. It was worth to watch, even though there was soem parts where I was just like ''Cmon! Do something!'' and that's how I broke my screen..
I'll rate it 7/10 even though idea is great and twist at the end is awesome. Also famous players acting there;)... BUT Mouse clicking by the guy who was currently filming was annoying as Spongebob's laugh while diarrhea after heavy drinking..
[size=24pt][b]MUST WATCH[/b][/size]
